{"tid":1388704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"釋放兩個人炸 你咁就滿足？","createTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T18:45:29.000Z","uid":201764,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc78b0f273af2e25201b3088306c67a3703016f2","tid":1388704,"uid":201764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"入面仲有唔止40幾位手足<br />\n依家班狗釋放兩個就打哂飛機？<br />\n我地要求嘅係齊上齊落 <br />\n一日入面仲有手足我地都唔可以滿足<br />\n即使放咗我地都要繼續要求5大訴求<br />\n<br />\n依家班狗打人嘅照打人<br />\n拉人又佢地話拉就拉<br />\n就連釋放都要我地去圍先至釋放<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會又尚未成立到<br />\n現時係無機制可以懲罰班狗<br />\n我見都有巴打搞外國聯署要求懲罰港共中央政府官員<br />\n不如諗下有咩手段可以懲罰埋班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"27256c01a4612a936a70f58150471be547b2ea40","tid":1388704,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"無一個無辜"},{"pid":"9c4b54c3db0ca9894a90798f8c3e647f376da32b","tid":1388704,"uid":201764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27256c01a4612a936a70f58150471be547b2ea40","tid":1388704,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"無一個無辜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:08:07.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差 當差正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3651fb4d9143e3b740fd7d1a96fefc67cb8e8a","tid":1388704,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c4b54c3db0ca9894a90798f8c3e647f376da32b","tid":1388704,"uid":201764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27256c01a4612a936a70f58150471be547b2ea40","tid":1388704,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"無一個無辜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:08:07.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差 當差正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\